<h2>Chapter 2: Dental Clinic Case Study — From Page 3 to Position 1 in 90 Days &#123;#ch2&#125;</h2>
<p>This case study comes from a dental clinic in Mumbai, India. The clinic had been open for 3 years but was invisible on Google. Patients found them through word of mouth or paid ads. Organic search drove almost zero new patient bookings.</p>
<h3>The Starting Point</h3>
<p>The clinic ranked on page 3 for "dentist Mumbai" and related terms. Their Google Business Profile had 12 reviews at 3.2 stars. The website was a basic template with no schema markup, no location-specific pages, and no content strategy.</p>
