<h3>The Strategy</h3>
<p>The campaign focused on 4 pillars: Google Business Profile overhaul, local landing pages, review generation, and technical SEO fixes.</p>
<p><strong>Google Business Profile optimization.</strong> The clinic claimed and verified their GBP. They selected the most accurate primary category ("Dentist") and added secondary categories ("Dental clinic," "Cosmetic dentist," "Emergency dental service"). They uploaded 50+ high-resolution photos of the clinic, staff, and procedures. They started posting weekly updates about dental tips, offers, and patient success stories.</p>
<p><strong>Local landing pages.</strong> They created dedicated pages for each service: teeth whitening, dental implants, root canal, braces, and emergency dentistry. Each page included local landmarks, directions from nearby neighborhoods, and patient testimonials from that area.</p>
<p><strong>Review generation system.</strong> After every appointment, the front desk sent a follow-up SMS with a direct link to the Google review page. They responded to every review within 24 hours. They also added a review request QR code at the reception desk.</p>
<p><strong>Technical SEO.</strong> They added LocalBusiness schema markup, fixed mobile responsiveness issues, improved page speed, and submitted an updated sitemap to Google.</p>
