<p><strong>Seasonal content calendar.</strong> They published content ahead of demand spikes: "How to Winterize Your Pipes in Austin" before cold snaps, "AC Maintenance Checklist for Texas Summers" before heat waves, and "What to Do When Your Water Heater Fails" as a year-round resource.</p>
