<p><strong>Review acceleration.</strong> They implemented a same-day review request system. After every completed job, the technician sent a text with a direct review link while still at the customer's home. They responded to every review with personalized messages.</p>
<p><strong>Local citations and backlinks.</strong> They built consistent listings on home service directories (HomeAdvisor, Angi, Thumbtack) and local business directories (Austin Chamber of Commerce, local neighborhood associations). They sponsored a local Little League team for a backlink and community visibility.</p>
